The paper discusses the definition and measurement of intelligence in the context of artificial intelligence, which is a core topic in the field of AI (cs.AI). The paper also surveys various tests of machine intelligence, which involves machine learning (cs.LG), robotics (cs.RO), neural networks (cs.NE), and computer vision (cs.CV).
